# Next.js 16 Simply

## Structure routes

```
src/app/
  page.tsx              → redirect /dashboard
  (app)/
    layout.tsx          → AppShell
    dashboard/page.tsx
    taches/page.tsx
    ...
```

## Règles Next 16

- `params` et `searchParams` = **Promises** → `await params`
- Middleware = `proxy.ts` (pas `middleware.ts`)
- `next.config.ts` : redirect `/login` → `/dashboard`

## Pages

Pages minces — déléguer à `components/{module}/{Module}View.tsx`.

```tsx
export default function BudgetPage() {
  return <BudgetView />;
}
```

## Config

- Turbopack dev
- `vercel.json` : `"framework": "nextjs"`
